&lt;Sarcasm&gt;You sure geared me well otherwise. All I have is due to you. The incredible weapon I wield! I mean hell, how many people are blessed at level 60 with a Stave of Shielding as their main weapon? And my Armor! ThurgQuest armor is better than ToV. And God knows I never got it from buying the MQ of it or going to get it with a single group before I joined tB. Thanks Santa Kurtis! You made every day like Christmas! &lt;/Sarcasm&gt;<br>
<br>
Now on to your other points. I NEVER begged for loot. In fact I don't remember other folks doing that either. We all worked our asses off and seem to have died just as often as anyone.<br>
<br>
Lets talk about loot for a minute. Who was it that HAD to have the haste earring from Rumblecrush? My God Kurtis! That was you! And you then sold out your account 2 weeks later? I’m glad that raised the value on your account on playerauctions for you. I guess we were the sell-outs since we stayed and fought to keep tB alive? Hey Kurtis? Isn’t tB your guild?<br>
<br>
