<br>
And as far as MIM went who was it again who pushed for the war? It sure as hell wasn’t me. You have done a great job Kurtis of selectively showing certain posts. Where is my post about how I thought it was a bad idea since we were so outnumbered and would have to fight dirty? What about your post about how everyone from all the other games were coming back to help out? What happened to the reinforcements from Asheron’s Call? DAoC? Shadowbane? Gosh….a couple people showed up but never seemed to be on when the PN guys were getting their asses handed to them due to numbers. I’m sorry, but as good as Scarre and Medivac are 2 vs. 20 just aren’t workable odds. Did certain people want Kory guilded? Yep. Did several others say “If you (That’s you Kurtis) are going to start a war with MIM then we should have Kory for his firepower?” yep. Hell, I don’t even know Kory other than chatting with him in game maybe 4 or 5 times.<br>
