<br>
Why am I mad? You are posting on things that you were not a part of. I am NOT mad you got to loot the cloak. I AM mad because you got loot and left the game and then rant about people leaving for loot. People who know me know I’m not loot driven. I play to see new things. I am very grateful of items I am given but it is not my reason for playing. So please don’t claim someone to be a loot whore until you know they are.<br>
